description: Horizons HTH seeks to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Solactive US 7-10 Year Treasury Bond CAD Hedged Index (Total Return), net of expenses. The Solactive US 7-10 Year Treasury Bond CAD Hedged Index (Total Return) is designed to measure the performance of the US 7-10 Year Treasury Bond market, hedged to the Canadian dollar.
name: Horizons US 7-10 Year Treasury Bond CAD Hedged ETF
